quran[18]{c,v,t,f}:
  37,136,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A pa àwọn yòókù run."
  37,137,"Dájúdájú ẹ̀yin náà kúkú ń gba ọ̀dọ̀ wọn kọjá láàárọ̀-láàárọ̀"
  37,138,"àti ní alaalẹ́. Ṣé ẹ kò níí ṣe làákàyè ni?"
  40,79,"Allāhu ni Ẹni tí Ó dá àwọn ẹran-ọ̀sìn fún yín nítorí kí ẹ lè máa gùn nínú wọn. Ẹ ó sì máa jẹ nínú wọn."
  40,80,"Àwọn àǹfààní (mìíràn) wà fún yín lára ẹran-ọ̀sìn. Àti nítorí kí ẹ lè dé ọ̀nà jíjìn tó wà lọ́kàn yín lórí (gígùn) wọ́n (kiri). Ẹ sì ń fi àwọn (ẹran-ọ̀sìn) àti ọkọ̀ ojú-omi gbé àwọn ẹrù."
  40,81,"(Allāhu) ń fi àwọn àmì Rẹ̀ hàn yín. Nítorí náà, èwo nínú àwọn àmì Allāhu l’ẹ máa takò?1 {1}",1:[Kíyè sí i! Àwọn asòòkùn sẹ́sìn àti àwọn onibidiah yóò máa pe iṣẹ́ aburú ọwọ́ wọn nípasẹ̀ idán pípa àti bidiah ṣíṣe ní “àmì Allāhu” láti lè ṣi àwọn ènìyàn lọ́nà. Kíyè sí i, ohunkóhun tí ó bá máa jẹ́ “àmì Allāhu / àmì Ọlọ́hun” kò níí fi ọ̀nà kan kan lòdì sí “āyah” kan kan nínú al-Ƙur’ān alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé nítorí pé, àwọn āyah al-Ƙur’ān alápọ̀n-ọ́nlé ni òṣùwọ̀n ìdáláre àti ìdálẹ́bi fún ohun tí ẹnikẹ́ni bá pè ní “àmì Ọlọ́hun”. Kódà, ohunkóhun tí ó bá máa jẹ́ “àmì Allāhu” kò níí fi ọ̀nà kan kan lòdì sí hadīth kan nínú àwọn hadīth Ànábì - kí ìkẹ́ àti ọlà Allāhu máa bá a - tó fẹsẹ̀ rinlẹ̀.]
  42,43,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá ṣe sùúrù, tí ó tún ṣàforíjìn, dájúdájú ìyẹn wà nínú àwọn ìpinnu ọ̀rọ̀."
  42,44,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí Allāhu bá ṣì lọ́nà, kò tún sí aláàbò kan fún un mọ́ lẹ́yìn Rẹ̀. O sì máa rí àwọn alábòsí nígbà tí wọ́n bá rí Iná, wọn yóò wí pé: “Ǹjẹ́ ọ̀nà kan kan wà tí a lè fi padà sí ilé ayé?”"
  42,45,"O sì máa rí wọn tí A máa kó wọn lọ sínú Iná; wọn yóò palọ́lọ́ láti ara ìyẹpẹrẹ, wọn yó si máa wò fín-ín-fín. Àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo sì máa sọ pé: “Dájúdájú àwọn ẹni òfò ni àwọn tó ṣe ẹ̀mí ara wọn àti ara ilé wọn ní òfò ní Ọjọ́ Àjíǹde.” Kíyè sí i, dájúdájú àwọn alábòsí yóò wà nínú ìyà gbére."
  43,25,"Nítorí náà, A gbẹ̀san lára wọn. Wo bí ìkángun àwọn tó pe òdodo ní irọ́ ti rí!"
  43,26,"(Rántí) nígbà tí (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm sọ fún bàbá rẹ̀ àti àwọn ènìyàn rẹ̀ pé: “Dájúdájú èmi yọwọ́ yọsẹ̀ kúrò nínú ohun tí ẹ̀ ń jọ́sìn fún."
  43,27,"Àfi Ẹni tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá mi. Dájúdájú Òun l’Ó máa fi ọ̀nà tààrà mọ̀ mí.”"
  44,10,"Nítorí náà, máa retí ọjọ́ tí sánmọ̀ yóò mú èéfín pọ́nńbélé wá."
  44,11,"Ó máa bo àwọn ènìyàn mọ́lẹ̀. Èyí ni ìyà ẹlẹ́ta-eléro."
  44,12,"(Àwọn ènìyàn yóò wí pé): Olúwa wa, gbé ìyà náà kúrò fún wa, dájúdájú àwa yóò gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo."
  45,1,"Hā mīm. (Allāhu ló mọ ohun tí Ó gbàlérò pẹ̀lú àwọn háràfí náà.)1 {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al Baƙọrah;  2:1.]
  45,2,"Tírà náà sọ̀kalẹ̀ díẹ̀ díẹ̀láti ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu, Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n. {1}",1:[Ẹ wo ìtọsẹ̀-ọ̀rọ̀ sūrah al-’Isrọ̄’;  17:106.]
  45,3,"Dájúdájú nínú àwọn sánmọ̀ àti ilẹ̀ àwọn àmì wà (nínú wọn) fún àwọn onígbàgbọ́ òdodo."